#: ca5c374e5ae5445cb679747982623db2
msgid "``src/``: Contains all the C++ source code for the firmware. *   ``main.cpp``: The main entry point of the application. Handles initialization and the main loop. *   ``ui*.cpp``: Source files related to the user interface, built with the LVGL library. *   ``system.cpp``: Manages system-level functions like time, battery, and WiFi. *   ``fs_helpers.cpp``: Helper functions for interacting with the SPIFFS filesystem. *   ``PSpref.cpp``: Manages persistent storage of settings in NVS (Non-Volatile Storage)."
